details.n: My Little Sister is an Osaka Momma

ratings.en: Saikin no Ôsaka okan bûmu wa dôyara ore no okage rashî desu yo
Imôto wa Ôsaka okan no megami-chan
Ôsaka okan na imôto to junan na ore
Konoucha ni hitori, Ôsaka okan ga iru!
Saikin, imôto no yôsu ga chotto Ôsaka okan nanda ga
Ôsaka okan dakedo ai saeareba kankeinai yo nê
Ore no imôto ga konnani Ôsaka okan na wakeganai
Imôto ga Ôsaka okan nandesu kedo!
Aru asa, Ôsaka okan no imôto ga dekimashite
